channel.title: Harbour - A Life-Changing Community (Android / iOS)
channel.description: Hey everyone, I'm James Gadsby, the developer of Harbour. Harbour is a life-changing community and app for people seeking newness in their lives. Every day, the world gets the same challenges to complete and share their stories. For those who are bored, adventurous or just stuck in a rut, Harbour’s guaranteed to make your day more interesting. Harbour is available for free on iOS and Android - check it out at harbour (dot) unicornplatform (dot) com :slight_smile:
